<body>
    <h1>Gourmet Sesame Black Garlic Noodles</h1>
    <p>Indulge in the rich, umami flavors of toasted sesame oil and black garlic oil with this exquisite noodle dish. The fusion of these specialty oils creates a symphony of savory notes that elevate this recipe to gourmet status.</p>

    <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>8 oz (225g) Asian wheat noodles</li>
        <li>2 tbsp toasted sesame oil</li>
        <li>1 tbsp black garlic oil</li>
        <li>2 cloves black garlic, minced</li>
        <li>2 tbsp soy sauce</li>
        <li>1 tsp honey</li>
        <li>1/2 tsp grated fresh ginger</li>
        <li>1/4 cup sliced green onions</li>
        <li>1 tbsp toasted sesame seeds</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions:</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Boil the noodles according to package instructions. Drain and rinse under cold water. Set aside.</li>
        <li>In a large bowl, whisk together the toasted sesame oil, black garlic oil, minced black garlic, soy sauce, honey, and grated ginger.</li>
        <li>Add the cooked noodles to the bowl and toss until well coated with the sauce.</li>
        <li>Garnish with sliced green onions and toasted sesame seeds before serving.</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="tips">
        <h3>Chef's Tips:</h3>
        <p>For an extra flavor boost, try adding a splash of black garlic balsamic vinegar to the sauce. It will add a delightful tanginess to the dish.</p>
        <p>Feel free to customize the toppings with shredded chicken, shrimp, or tofu for a protein-packed variation.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="serving">
        <h3>Serving Suggestions:</h3>
        <p>Pair these gourmet noodles with a crisp cucumber salad and a glass of chilled white wine for a luxurious dining experience.</p>
    </div>
</body>
